{"id":1590,"date":"2024-01-05T14:18:54","date_gmt":"2024-01-05T14:18:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/ozkocakhafriyat.com.tr\/?page_id=1590"},"modified":"2024-01-10T12:33:44","modified_gmt":"2024-01-10T12:33:44","slug":"tum-hafriyat-isleri","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/ozkocakhafriyat.com.tr\/tum-hafriyat-isleri\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u00fcm Hafriyat \u0130\u015fleri"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text]<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright wp-image-1640 \" src=\"https:\/\/ozkocakhafriyat.com.tr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/oz-kocak-hafriyat-13-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"538\" height=\"403\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ozkocakhafriyat.com.tr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/oz-kocak-hafriyat-13-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/ozkocakhafriyat.com.tr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/oz-kocak-hafriyat-13-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ozkocakhafriyat.com.tr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/oz-kocak-hafriyat-13-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ozkocakhafriyat.com.tr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/oz-kocak-hafriyat-13-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ozkocakhafriyat.com.tr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/oz-kocak-hafriyat-13.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 538px) 100vw, 538px\" \/>Hafriyat i\u015fleri, genellikle in\u015faat ve altyap\u0131 projelerinde kullan\u0131lan, arazi d\u00fczenlemesi ve malzeme ta\u015f\u0131ma gibi \u00e7e\u015fitli faaliyetleri i\u00e7eren bir in\u015faat sekt\u00f6r\u00fc kategorisidir. <span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Hafriyat i\u015fleri, genellikle b\u00fcy\u00fck \u00f6l\u00e7ekli in\u015faat projelerinde kullan\u0131lan \u00f6nemli bir hizmettir. Bu i\u015fler, in\u015faat projelerinin ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 bir \u015fekilde tamamlanabilmesi ve istenen altyap\u0131y\u0131 olu\u015fturabilmek i\u00e7in kilit bir rol oynar. Hafriyat i\u015fleri, geni\u015f bir yelpazede teknolojik ekipman ve uzmanl\u0131k gerektiren bir aland\u0131r.<\/span><\/p>\n<div class=\"w-full text-token-text-primary\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-7\">\n<div class=\"px-4 py-2 justify-center text-base md:gap-6 m-auto\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-1 text-base mx-auto gap-3 md:px-5 lg:px-1 xl:px-5 md:max-w-3xl lg:max-w-[40rem] xl:max-w-[48rem] group\">\n<div class=\"relative flex w-full flex-col lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)] agent-turn\">\n<div class=\"flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-grow flex-col max-w-full\">\n<div class=\"min-h-[20px] text-message flex flex-col items-start gap-3 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5 overflow-x-auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"20ee7763-6ebb-4fa7-8156-aec6375f3295\">\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\">\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Toprak Kaz\u0131s\u0131 ve Dolgu \u0130\u015fleri:<\/strong> Arsa d\u00fczenlemesi i\u00e7in mevcut topraklar\u0131n kaz\u0131lmas\u0131, d\u00fczenlenmesi ve dolgu yap\u0131lmas\u0131 i\u015flemlerini kapsar. Bu, bina temelleri, otoparklar, yollar veya di\u011fer altyap\u0131 projeleri i\u00e7in arazi haz\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 anlam\u0131na gelir.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Temel Kaz\u0131lar\u0131:<\/strong> \u0130n\u015fa edilecek binalar\u0131n veya yap\u0131lar\u0131n temelleri i\u00e7in gerekli olan toprak kaz\u0131lar\u0131. Bu, bina projelerinin temel altyap\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 olu\u015fturmak i\u00e7in \u00f6nemli bir ad\u0131md\u0131r.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Kanal A\u00e7ma \u0130\u015fleri:<\/strong> Su, kanalizasyon veya ileti\u015fim hatlar\u0131 gibi altyap\u0131 tesislerinin d\u00f6\u015fenmesi i\u00e7in toprak kaz\u0131lar\u0131 yap\u0131lmas\u0131.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Baraj \u0130n\u015faat\u0131 ve G\u00f6let Kaz\u0131lar\u0131:<\/strong> Su depolama projeleri i\u00e7in b\u00fcy\u00fck \u00f6l\u00e7ekli toprak kaz\u0131lar\u0131 ve dolgu i\u015flemleri. Barajlar veya g\u00f6letler, su kaynaklar\u0131n\u0131 kontrol alt\u0131na almak ve suyun depolanmas\u0131 i\u00e7in kullan\u0131l\u0131r.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Madencilik Hafriyat \u0130\u015fleri:<\/strong> Madenlerde kullan\u0131lmak \u00fczere maden yataklar\u0131n\u0131n a\u00e7\u0131lmas\u0131, madenlerde malzeme \u00e7\u0131kar\u0131lmas\u0131 ve bu malzemenin i\u015flenmesi.<\/li>\n<li><strong>\u00c7evre D\u00fczenleme Projeleri:<\/strong> Parklar, rekreasyon alanlar\u0131 veya do\u011fal ya\u015fam alanlar\u0131 olu\u015fturmak i\u00e7in toprak d\u00fczenleme i\u015flemleri.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Kaz\u0131 \u0130\u015flemleri \u0130\u00e7in Makine Kiralama:<\/strong> B\u00fcy\u00fck \u00f6l\u00e7ekli hafriyat i\u015flerinde kullan\u0131lmak \u00fczere kazma, y\u00fckleyici ve benzeri makinelerin kiralanmas\u0131.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Toprak Islah ve Stabilizasyon \u0130\u015fleri:<\/strong> Zeminin istenen \u00f6zelliklere getirilmesi i\u00e7in yap\u0131lan \u00e7al\u0131\u015fmalar. Topra\u011f\u0131n stabilize edilmesi veya \u0131slah edilmesi, in\u015faat projeleri i\u00e7in zeminin dayan\u0131kl\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 art\u0131rabilir.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"title1\">Hafriyat Nedir?<\/h2>\n<p>Hafriyat, in\u015faat alan\u0131nda yap\u0131lan t\u00fcm kaz\u0131 i\u015fleri ve kaz\u0131 sonras\u0131 \u00e7\u0131kar\u0131lan malzemenin \u015fantiye alan\u0131ndan uzakla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131larak belirli alanlara d\u00f6k\u00fclmesi gibi i\u015fleri kapsayan i\u015flemlerdir. Hafriyat i\u015fleri belediye kontrol\u00fcnde olmal\u0131 ve izinsiz yap\u0131lmamal\u0131d\u0131r.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"title2\">Hafriyat Uygulamas\u0131 Nas\u0131l Yap\u0131l\u0131r?<\/h2>\n<p>Hafriyat i\u015fleri kazma, k\u00fcrek kullan\u0131larak y\u0131llarca yap\u0131ld\u0131. Geli\u015fen teknolojiyle beraber bu i\u015fler a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131kl\u0131 olarak i\u015f makinalar\u0131yla yap\u0131lmaya devam ediliyor. Kep\u00e7e, ekskavat\u00f6r gibi i\u015f makinalar\u0131 hafriyat i\u015flerinde a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131kla kullan\u0131lan ara\u00e7lar. Bu ara\u00e7lar sayesinde hafriyat i\u015flemi h\u0131zl\u0131 ve g\u00fcvenli \u015fekilde yap\u0131l\u0131yor. Hafriyat uygulamas\u0131 i\u015flem uygulanacak olan yere g\u00f6re de\u011fi\u015fkenlik g\u00f6sterebilir, bunun i\u00e7in bir\u00e7ok y\u00f6ntem mevcuttur. Kaz\u0131 y\u00f6ntemi belirlendikten sonra kullan\u0131lacak malzemeler ve i\u015f makinalar\u0131 belirlenir.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Kaz\u0131 i\u015flemine ba\u015flamadan \u00f6nce detayl\u0131 zemin et\u00fcd\u00fc yap\u0131l\u0131r ve uygun kaz\u0131 y\u00f6ntemi belirlenir.<\/li>\n<li>Kaz\u0131 i\u015flemi \u015fevli veya iksal\u0131 yap\u0131l\u0131r. Bu sayede \u00e7\u00f6kme veya kayma engellenir.<\/li>\n<li>Kazma, k\u00fcrek veya i\u015f makinalar\u0131 ile kaz\u0131 i\u015flemi yap\u0131l\u0131rken \u00e7\u0131kar\u0131lan malzeme \u00f6ncelikle g\u00fcvenli bir \u015fekilde hafriyat kamyonlar\u0131na y\u00fcklenir.<\/li>\n<li>Hafriyat kamyonlar\u0131 t\u00fcm malzemeyi d\u00f6k\u00fcm alan\u0131na g\u00f6t\u00fcr\u00fcr ve d\u00f6ker. Bu i\u015flem hafriyat i\u015fi bitene kadar tekrarlan\u0131r.<\/li>\n<li>Kaz\u0131 s\u0131ras\u0131nda \u00e7\u0131kar\u0131lan malzeme incelenir, kimyasal at\u0131k olup olmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 uzman ki\u015filerce kontrol edilir.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"title3\">Hafriyat Uygulamas\u0131nda Dikkat Edilmesi Gereken Detaylar Nelerdir?<\/h2>\n<p>Hafriyat uygulamas\u0131 ciddi \u00f6nlemler gerektirir. \u0130\u015f sa\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve g\u00fcvenli\u011fi kurallar\u0131n\u0131n en \u00fcst seviyede uygulanmas\u0131 gerekir. Bu do\u011frultuda dikkat edilmesi gereken hususlar \u00e7evre ve \u015fehircilik bakanl\u0131\u011f\u0131 y\u00f6netmeli\u011fi kurallar\u0131nda a\u00e7\u0131k\u00e7a belirtilmi\u015ftir.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/cygm.csb.gov.tr\/yonetmelikler-i-440\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">(https:\/\/cygm.csb.gov.tr\/yonetmelikler-i-440)<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u00d6ncelikle dikkat edilmesi gereken hususlara de\u011finecek olursak;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0130\u015f sa\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve g\u00fcvenli\u011fi kurallar\u0131 eksiksiz uygulanmal\u0131.<\/li>\n<li>\u015eantiye sahas\u0131 kontrol alt\u0131na al\u0131nmal\u0131 ve \u00e7evreyle ba\u011flant\u0131n\u0131n kesilmeli.<\/li>\n<li>\u00c7evreye verilebilecek zararlar\u0131 \u00f6nceden tespit edip gerekli \u00f6nlemler al\u0131nmal\u0131.<\/li>\n<li>Hafriyat malzemesinin \u015fantiyeden g\u00f6nderilmesi koordine edilmeli.<\/li>\n<li>Kaz\u0131 i\u015fleminin projesine uygun \u015fekilde yap\u0131lmal\u0131 teknik ekip taraf\u0131ndan s\u00fcrekli takip edilmeli.<\/li>\n<li>Kaz\u0131 i\u015flemi \u00f6ncesi t\u00fcm altyap\u0131 ba\u011flant\u0131lar\u0131 belirlenmeli ve bu ba\u011flant\u0131lara zarar verilmemeli.<\/li>\n<li>T\u00fcm hafriyat i\u015fleri alan\u0131nda uzman ki\u015fi veya kurumlarca yap\u0131lmal\u0131.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"title4\">K\u0131r\u0131m ve Y\u0131k\u0131m \u0130\u015fi Nedir?<\/h2>\n<p>Bir yap\u0131y\u0131 yeni bir g\u00f6r\u00fcn\u00fcme kavu\u015fturmak i\u00e7in \u00f6ncelikle istenmeyen mevcut par\u00e7alar\u0131n k\u0131r\u0131m ve y\u0131k\u0131m\u0131 yap\u0131l\u0131r. Bu i\u015flem her t\u00fcrl\u00fc tadilat, yenileme i\u015flerinin ilk basama\u011f\u0131d\u0131r.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"title5\">K\u0131r\u0131m ve Y\u0131k\u0131m \u0130\u015fi Nas\u0131l Yap\u0131l\u0131r?<\/h2>\n<p>K\u0131r\u0131m ve y\u0131k\u0131m i\u015fleri her projeye g\u00f6re de\u011fi\u015fkenlik g\u00f6sterir. Bu i\u015flem geri d\u00f6n\u00fc\u015f\u00fc olmayan sonu\u00e7lara yol a\u00e7abilece\u011fi i\u00e7in \u00f6ncelikle y\u0131k\u0131m yap\u0131lacak olan yap\u0131 detayl\u0131 incelenir ve mevcut durum raporu \u00e7\u0131kar\u0131l\u0131r. Bu rapora g\u00f6re yap\u0131 dayan\u0131m\u0131na zarar vermeyecek \u015fekilde planlama yap\u0131l\u0131r ve y\u0131k\u0131m projesi olu\u015fturulur.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Y\u0131k\u0131m projesine g\u00f6re teknik ekip duvar, beton, seramik vb. kaplama malzemeleri gibi k\u0131r\u0131m\u0131 yap\u0131lacak par\u00e7alar\u0131 belirler. Bu do\u011frultuda belirlenen i\u015fler uzman ekipler taraf\u0131ndan \u00f6zenle yap\u0131l\u0131r.<\/li>\n<li>Yap\u0131lacak i\u015fe g\u00f6re kullan\u0131lan aletler belirlenir. K\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m balyoz, kazma gibi el aletleriyle veya k\u0131r\u0131c\u0131, delici hiltilerle yap\u0131l\u0131r.<\/li>\n<li>K\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m sonras\u0131 ortaya \u00e7\u0131kan moloz malzeme \u00e7al\u0131\u015fma alan\u0131ndan uzakla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131l\u0131r. Moloz malzemesi el arabalar\u0131yla veya \u00e7uvallanarak moloz arabas\u0131na ta\u015f\u0131n\u0131r.<\/li>\n<li>G\u00fcvenle moloz y\u00fcklemesi yap\u0131ld\u0131ktan sonra moloz arabas\u0131 d\u00f6k\u00fcm alan\u0131na nakledilir. Bu i\u015flem k\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m i\u015fi bitene kadar tekrarlan\u0131r.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"title6\">K\u0131r\u0131m ve Y\u0131k\u0131m Maliyetleri Nelere G\u00f6re De\u011fi\u015fim G\u00f6sterir?<\/h2>\n<p>K\u0131r\u0131m ve y\u0131k\u0131m i\u015fleri maliyeti her projeye g\u00f6re de\u011fi\u015fkenlik g\u00f6sterir. Her proje kendine \u00f6zeldir ve k\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m uygulama \u015fekli farkl\u0131d\u0131r. Maliyetlere etki edecek baz\u0131 unsurlara de\u011finecek olursak;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>K\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m i\u015fini yapmak i\u00e7in gerekli insan g\u00fcc\u00fc<\/li>\n<li>K\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m i\u015fini yapmak i\u00e7in gerekli el aletleri ve hilti gibi makinalar\u0131n ne derecede kullan\u0131laca\u011f\u0131<\/li>\n<li>K\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m i\u015flemi sonras\u0131 ortaya \u00e7\u0131kan molozun nakliye ara\u00e7lar\u0131na ta\u015f\u0131nma \u015fekli<\/li>\n<li>K\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m yap\u0131lacak yerin d\u00f6k\u00fcm alan\u0131na uzakl\u0131\u011f\u0131<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"title7\">K\u0131r\u0131m ve Y\u0131k\u0131m \u0130\u015flerinde Dikkat Edilmesi Gereken Detaylar Nelerdir?<\/h2>\n<p>K\u0131r\u0131m ve y\u0131k\u0131m i\u015fleri \u00f6zenle yap\u0131lmad\u0131\u011f\u0131 taktirde geri d\u00f6n\u00fc\u015f\u00fc olmayan sonu\u00e7lara yol a\u00e7abilir. Bu i\u015fler can ve mal kay\u0131plar\u0131 ya\u015famamak i\u00e7in alan\u0131nda uzman ekipler taraf\u0131ndan yap\u0131lmal\u0131d\u0131r.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>K\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m i\u015fleri yap\u0131lmadan \u00f6nce teknik ekipler gerekli t\u00fcm analizleri yapmal\u0131, yap\u0131 dayan\u0131m\u0131n\u0131 etkileyecek uygulamalardan ka\u00e7\u0131n\u0131lmal\u0131<\/li>\n<li>Yap\u0131lacak i\u015f i\u00e7in kullan\u0131lacak malzemeler do\u011fru se\u00e7ilmeli<\/li>\n<li>Yap\u0131 ve \u00e7evresine gerekli koruma \u00f6nlemleri al\u0131nmal\u0131<\/li>\n<li>K\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m i\u015fleri alan\u0131nda yetkin ki\u015filerce yap\u0131lmal\u0131<\/li>\n<li>Hem ekonomik hem g\u00fcvenli k\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m ve moloz ta\u015f\u0131ma planlamas\u0131 yap\u0131lmal\u0131<\/li>\n<li>K\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m i\u015fi boyunca teknik ekip kontrolleri ger\u00e7ekle\u015ftirmeli<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"title8\">K\u0131r\u0131m ve Y\u0131k\u0131m \u0130\u015fleri \u0130\u00e7in Nereye Ba\u015fvurulur ve Nas\u0131l Bir Yol \u0130zlenir?<\/h2>\n<p>K\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m ve tadilat i\u015fleri i\u00e7in ilgili belediyelerden ruhsat almak gerekir. \u00d6ncelikle uzman kurumlardan yap\u0131lacak i\u015fler i\u00e7in destek al\u0131nmal\u0131d\u0131r. \u0130zinsiz k\u0131r\u0131m y\u0131k\u0131m ve tadilat i\u015fleri yap\u0131lmamal\u0131d\u0131r. Ruhsat ba\u015fvurusu araca kurumlarla yap\u0131labildi\u011fi gibi do\u011frudan mal sahibi taraf\u0131ndan da yap\u0131labilir. \u00d6ncelikle belediyeye dilek\u00e7e ile m\u00fcracaat edilir.<\/p>\n<p>Ruhsat ba\u015fvurusu i\u00e7in gereken belgeler;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tapu kay\u0131t \u00f6rne\u011fi (son ay tarih onayl\u0131)<\/li>\n<li>Tadilat projeleri<\/li>\n<li>Proje m\u00fcellifi onay\u0131<\/li>\n<li>Bakanl\u0131k\u00e7a izin belgesi alm\u0131\u015f laboratuvar ortam\u0131nda yap\u0131lm\u0131\u015f karot + demir deney sonu\u00e7lar\u0131 belgesi<\/li>\n<li>Yap\u0131 Denetim \u015eirketi&#8217;nden al\u0131nm\u0131\u015f uygunluk raporu<\/li>\n<li>Yap\u0131 Denetim onayl\u0131 g\u00fc\u00e7lendirme projesi<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"title9\">Moloz Ta\u015f\u0131ma Nas\u0131l Yap\u0131l\u0131r?<\/h2>\n<p>\u00d6ncelikle ta\u015f\u0131nacak moloz ve ta\u015f\u0131ma yap\u0131lacak y\u00f6ntem belirlenir. Uygun ta\u015f\u0131ma y\u00f6ntemi belirlendikten sonra bu konuda uzman ki\u015filer i\u015f alan\u0131na gelir ve ta\u015f\u0131ma i\u015flemi yap\u0131l\u0131r. Ta\u015f\u0131ma i\u015flemi yap\u0131l\u0131rken t\u00fcm g\u00fcvenlik \u00f6nlemleri al\u0131nmal\u0131d\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p>K\u0131r\u0131m, y\u0131k\u0131m, hafriyat i\u015feri sonras\u0131 ortaya \u00e7\u0131kan moloz y\u0131\u011f\u0131nlar\u0131n\u0131n i\u015f alan\u0131ndan uzakla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131lmas\u0131 gerekir. Bu i\u015fler uygulaman\u0131n yap\u0131laca\u011f\u0131 i\u015f sahas\u0131na g\u00f6re de\u011fi\u015fir. \u00c7al\u0131\u015fma rahatl\u0131\u011f\u0131 olan alanlarda jcb, ekskavat\u00f6r gibi i\u015f makinalar\u0131yla moloz y\u00fcklemesi moloz arabas\u0131na yap\u0131l\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p>\u0130\u015f makinelerinin giremeyece\u011fi alanlarda insan g\u00fcc\u00fc kullan\u0131l\u0131r. Moloz ta\u015f\u0131ma s\u0131ras\u0131nda el arabas\u0131, asans\u00f6r gibi elemanlarla ta\u015f\u0131n\u0131r ve moloz kamyonuna y\u00fcklenir. El arabas\u0131 kullan\u0131lamayan alanlarda ise moloz \u00e7uvallanarak ta\u015f\u0131n\u0131r ve moloz kamyonuna y\u00fcklenir. Y\u00fckleme i\u015flemi tamamland\u0131ktan sonra moloz kamyonu uygun d\u00f6k\u00fcm alan\u0131na g\u00f6nderilir. Bu i\u015flem t\u00fcm moloz g\u00f6nderilene kadar tekrarlan\u0131r.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"title10\">Moloz Ta\u015f\u0131ma \u00dccretleri Nelere G\u00f6re De\u011fi\u015fiklik G\u00f6sterir?<\/h2>\n<p>Moloz ta\u015f\u0131ma \u00fccretleri bir\u00e7ok fakt\u00f6re g\u00f6re de\u011fi\u015fkenlik g\u00f6sterir. Bu konuda bir fiyat bi\u00e7mek i\u00e7in \u00f6ncelikle bu de\u011fi\u015fkenliklerin tespiti yap\u0131lmal\u0131d\u0131r. Moloz ta\u015f\u0131ma \u00fccretlerini etkileyen ba\u015fl\u0131ca maddeler \u015funlard\u0131r;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Molozun ta\u015f\u0131ma y\u00f6ntemi<\/li>\n<li>Molozun i\u00e7eri\u011fi<\/li>\n<li>Molozun ta\u015f\u0131ma mesafesi<\/li>\n<li>\u0130\u015f alan\u0131n\u0131n moloz d\u00f6k\u00fcm sahas\u0131na olan uzakl\u0131\u011f\u0131<\/li>\n<li>Moloz ta\u015f\u0131mas\u0131nda kullan\u0131lacak i\u015f makinalar\u0131 ve el aletleri<\/li>\n<li>Moloz ta\u015f\u0131mas\u0131 i\u00e7in \u00e7al\u0131\u015fabilecek i\u015f\u00e7i say\u0131s\u0131<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u00d6z Kocak Hafriyat olarak t\u00fcm ya\u015fam alanlar\u0131nda yapmak istedi\u011finiz de\u011fi\u015fiklikler i\u00e7in k\u0131r\u0131m, y\u0131k\u0131m, moloz at\u0131m\u0131 ve hafriyat i\u015flerini \u00f6zenle ger\u00e7ekle\u015ftiriyoruz. Hafriyat ve k\u0131r\u0131m i\u015flerini i\u015f g\u00fcvenli\u011fi risklerini g\u00f6z ard\u0131 etmeden tamaml\u0131yoruz.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text]Hafriyat i\u015fleri, genellikle in\u015faat ve altyap\u0131 projelerinde kullan\u0131lan, arazi d\u00fczenlemesi ve malzeme ta\u015f\u0131ma gibi \u00e7e\u015fitli faaliyetleri i\u00e7eren bir in\u015faat sekt\u00f6r\u00fc kategorisidir. Hafriyat i\u015fleri, genellikle b\u00fcy\u00fck \u00f6l\u00e7ekli in\u015faat projelerinde kullan\u0131lan \u00f6nemli bir hizmettir. Bu i\u015fler, in\u015faat projelerinin ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 bir \u015fekilde tamamlanabilmesi ve istenen altyap\u0131y\u0131 olu\u015fturabilmek i\